name: THE_F00L/GENESIS
description:
survived a toxic environment, and a pandemic storm that never abated.
armed with knowledge from cyberspace, enthusiasm and recommendations from friends across the alpha wave
trying to get back to the surface for grinding and looting to protect my own vault... my own fortess, preparing for another cataclysm
still too afraid to take off this safety suit... um i called it heavy armor
still too stupid to kill the infected
still too naive to start a new quest
